left','Bolon地板由39%碳酸钙，37%PVC、18%增塑剂、2%玻璃纤维、2%稳定剂以及1%颜料组成。从化石的角度讲，Bolon地板包含33%的化石原料，主要是增塑剂和PVC，其余67%为无机材料，大部分为来自地壳中常见的盐。\r\nBolon所采用的PVC是一种由57%的盐和43%石油组合成的聚合物。这种PVC坚固耐用，不含任何有毒物质，比如邻苯二甲酸酯、重金属。'),(41629,285,'_material_5_description_0_left','field_629852f727aa5'),(41630,285,'material_5_description_0_right','与其他普通PVC相比，因为含盐量高，所以化石原料的含量较少，独特的聚合物结构可以做到100%回收，不仅能重复回收利用多次，还能满足长久使用的需求，因此Bolon所有的产品都享有10或15年的质保期。'),(41631,285,'_material_5_description_0_right','field_629852f727aa6'),(41632,285,'material_5_description_1_image','45'),(41633,285,'_material_5_description_1_image','field_629852f727aa7'),(41634,285,'material_5_description_2_full','*Bolon所有使用的PVC只从符合最佳环境实践 PVC 要求的乙烯基制造商处购买。并且这些工厂需要同样参与工厂节能计划，生产过程中污染排放量小。(该段文字以小字展示)'),(41635,285,'_material_5_description_2_full','field_629852f727aa4'),(41636,285,'material_5_description','a:3:{i:0;s:4:\"twin\";i:1;s:5:\"image\";i:2;s:6:\"single\";}'),(41637,285,'_material_5_description','field_629852f727aa3'),(41638,285,'chemical_3_title','Bolon无毒地板的发展过程'),(41639,285,'_chemical_3_title','field_629855620fc4d'),(41640,285,'chemical_3_description',''),(41641,285,'_chemical_3_description','field_629855620fc4e'),(41642,285,'chemical_3_card_0_number','2003'),(41643,285,'_chemical_3_card_0_number','field_629855620fc50'),(41644,285,'chemical_3_card_0_suffix',''),(41645,285,'_chemical_3_card_0_suffix','field_629855620fc51'),(41646,285,'chemical_3_card_0_description','逐步淘汰使用铅作为稳定剂'),(41647,285,'_chemical_3_card_0_description','field_629855620fc52'),(41648,285,'chemical_3_card_0_tag',''),(41649,285,'_chemical_3_card_0_tag','field_629855620fc53'),(41650,285,'chemical_3_card_1_number','2010'),(41651,285,'_chemical_3_card_1_number','field_629855620fc50'),(41652,285,'chemical_3_card_1_suffix',''),(41653,285,'_chemical_3_card_1_suffix','field_629855620fc51'),(41654,285,'chemical_3_card_1_description','为部分产品开发不含领苯二甲酸酯和无化石基的增塑剂'),(41655,285,'_chemical_3_card_1_description','field_629855620fc52'),(41656,285,'chemical_3_card_1_tag',''),(41657,285,'_chemical_