机器无法使用的区域，我们可采用手动清洁的方式。日常的简单清洁我们只需使用吸尘器、拖把、软毛刷、温水进行清洁即可。清洁频率可根据环境情况而定，顽固脏污需采取特殊清洁剂处理，请参考（污渍处理）。'),(42983,2244,'_clean_video_0_content_description','field_629dbd3526808'),(42984,2244,'clean_video_0_content_list',''),(42985,2244,'_clean_video_0_content_list','field_629dbd3526809'),(42986,2244,'clean_video_0_content',''),(42987,2244,'_clean_video_0_content','field_629dbd3526807'),(42988,2244,'clean_video_0_video_0_image','50'),(42989,2244,'_clean_video_0_video_0_image','field_629dbd352680c'),(42990,2244,'clean_video_0_video_0_url','https://youtu.be/8D2fVLGw2SU'),(42991,2244,'_clean_video_0_video_0_url','field_629dbd352680d'),(42992,2244,'clean_video_0_video_1_image','55'),(42993,2244,'_clean_video_0_video_1_image','field_629dbd352680c'),(42994,2244,'clean_video_0_video_1_url','https://youtu.be/dQw4w9WgXcQ'),(42995,2244,'_clean_video_0_video_1_url','field_629dbd352680d'),(42996,2244,'clean_video_0_video','2'),(42997,2244,'_clean_video_0_video','field_629dbd352680b'),(42998,2244,'clean_video_1_title','深度清洁'),(42999,2244,'_clean_video_1_title','field_629dbd3526806'),(43000,2244,'clean_video_1_content_description','除日常的简单清洁外，深度清洁可以帮助地板恢复到更好状态。较小面积区域或无法使用机器的区域，可采取手动深度清洁的方式，大面积区域可以采用机器清洁：'),(43001,2244,'_clean_video_1_content_description','field_629dbd3526808'),(43002,2244,'clean_video_1_content_list_0_item','先使用吸尘器清除表面灰尘后，去除地板上各种顽固污渍，请参考（污渍处理）'),(43003,2244,'_clean_video_1_content_list_0_item','field_629dbd352680a'),(43004,2244,'clean_video_1_content_list_1_item','再使用软毛刷或者洗地机、温水和少量多功能清洁剂（pH8-11）对地面进行刷洗，刷洗方向尽量沿着地板纵向纹理进行'),(43005,2244,'_clean_video_1_content_list_1_item','field_629dbd352680a'),(43006,2244,'clean_video_1_content_list_2_item','待清洁剂作用5-10分钟后，在使用清水清洗1-2次，直至没有泡沫'),(43007,2244,'_clean_video_1_content_list_2_item','field_629dbd352680a'),(43008,2244,'clean_video_1_content_list','3'),(43009,2244,'_clean_video_1_content_list','field_629dbd3526809'),(43010,2244,'clean_video_1_content',''),(43011,2244,'_clean_video_1_content','field_629dbd3526807'),(43012,2244,'clean_vid